protected class DOMAdapterFactoryContentProvider.LoadListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IWsDomLoadListener

Class that is used to listen when the DOM load will be finished. After the load has finished this class traverses the project explorers tree in order to find all instances of ILoadingWsProject and substitute them with loaded IWebServiceProject
